net.java.slee.resource.http
Interface HttpServletRequestActivity

All Known Implementing Classes:
HttpServletRequestActivityImpl
public interface HttpServletRequestActivity

HttpServletRequestActivity represents an incoming javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest. The implementing ResourceAdaptor ends the activity after posting the request event that created the activity.
